{"tid":1987714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"白兵vs連登仔","createTime":"2020-04-24T16:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T18:14:55.000Z","uid":305212,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d025e5a72e60e49f9bfeb71095b6f9eab5af095a","tid":1987714,"uid":305212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"白兵論述：<br />\n<br />\n立法會贏唔到嘅原因係所有選舉資源都係港共度<br />\n登記選民&mdash;&gt;拖你個申請程序<br />\n<br />\n登記到選民，啲人參選&mdash;&gt;dq參選資格，連閘都入唔到<br />\n<br />\n就算比入到閘&mdash;&gt;有邊啲組別會贏到？(港共到做緊野架，增加選民)<br />\n<br />\n就算比你贏左&mdash;&gt;搞財政懸崖嗰陣直接拉走幾個泛民，比財政預算案過到<br />\n<br />\n就算製造財政懸崖成功左&mdash;&gt;緊急法，搞個臨時立法會，點挽？<br />\n<br />\n泛民嘅主張成功嘅話，係要以上所有 係所有條件都過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 雖則phone in連登仔輸左 但都勇氣可嘉 係有勇氣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"958892467b76deca07c1bff185400063fb1c408c","tid":1987714,"uid":305212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec17db7f7853ce4213151cd0662a28b365770c9d","tid":1987714,"uid":182222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以喺雙線發展？<br />\n短期內要爭取功能組別，攞翻立法會制衡權力<br />\n長期爭取雙普選<br />\n其實兩樣嘢冇衝突"},{"pid":"dc5514e8b45bd691bf414bfe2098f626ae3c618e","tid":1987714,"uid":305857,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec17db7f7853ce4213151cd0662a28b365770c9d","tid":1987714,"uid":182222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以喺雙線發展？<br />\n短期內要爭取功能組別，攞翻立法會制衡權力<br />\n長期爭取雙普選<br />\n其實兩樣嘢冇衝突"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"你完全冇駁過白兵啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf34006c3309a76621a661bef2ff4b0265683ce9","tid":1987714,"uid":25089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec17db7f7853ce4213151cd0662a28b365770c9d","tid":1987714,"uid":182222,"like":2,"dislike":4,